# Sephr — 017-builtin-ublock-origin
#
# Ships uBlock Origin as a built-in component extension. The unpacked
# extension is fetched at bootstrap (scripts/fetch_ublock_origin.sh) and
# copied into the framework Resources/ by package_framework.py.
#
